          <mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="700" color="#ffffff" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="30px">Are you looking for an exciting and
enriching opportunity to expand your
knowledge while immersing yourself in
a vibrant culture? </mj-text>  


          <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="300" color="#ffffff" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="22px">Join our <strong>2-week study programme in Malaysia</strong> for an
unforgettable adventure where you'll have the chance to
participate in a wide range of activities such as <strong>cultural
workshops</strong>, <strong>language classes</strong>, and <strong>discovery tours</strong>. These
activities will not only <strong>deepen your understanding and
appreciation</strong> of <strong>Malaysian customs and traditions</strong>, but also
provide you with <strong>valuable skills and experiences</strong> that you can
apply to your studies and future career.</mj-text> 

<mj-spacer height="20px" />


<mj-image align="left"  padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" padding-right="30px" padding-top="0px"  src="https://i.ibb.co/L1RhfQX/why-malaysia.png"width="170px"></mj-image>
<mj-spacer height="20px" />
<mj-image align="left"  padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" padding-right="30px" padding-top="0px"  src="https://i.ibb.co/tcBS9CB/why-1.png"width="500px"></mj-image>
<mj-spacer height="20px" />
<mj-image align="left"  padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" padding-right="30px" padding-top="0px"  src="https://i.ibb.co/23MVN9t/why-2.png"width="500px"></mj-image>
