        <mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="700" color="#134473" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="30px">Programme 1: Understanding Malaysia </mj-text>  
        
      

        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="300" color="#134473" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="22px">Our programme is specifically designed for <strong>international students</strong> who are
interested in <strong>learning the Malay language</strong> and <strong>understanding Malaysian
culture</strong>! Throughout the week, you will be introduced to the fundamentals of
<strong>Malay vocabulary</strong>, <strong>grammar</strong>, <strong>pronunciation</strong>, <strong>writing skills</strong> &amp; <strong>cultural studies</strong>.

</mj-text> 

<mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="300" color="#134473" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="22px">Our <strong>interactive activities and exercises</strong> provide ample opportunities for you
to practice what you have learned. You'll be equipped with knowledge in
<strong>Malay language and culture</strong> that establishes a solid foundation, enabling you
to confidently engage with <strong>Malaysian cultures and communities</strong>.

</mj-text> 

<mj-spacer height="10px" />
        
        
        <mj-image align="center"  padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="30px" padding-right="30px" padding-top="0px"  src="https://i.ibb.co/pP6qxpQ/programme-1.png"width="600px"></mj-image>
  

    

        </mj-column>


        </mj-section>

        <!--programme-->

        <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border="none" padding-bottom="0" padding-left="30px" padding-right="30px" >
        <mj-column width="100%">
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-image align="center"  padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="25px" padding-right="25px" padding-top="0px"  src="https://i.ibb.co/mcpzL6N/line-dark.png"width="600px"></mj-image>
        <mj-text font-size="22px" font-weight="700" color="#134473" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="30px">Programme 2: Discovering Malaysia</mj-text>  
        
      

        <mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="300" color="#134473" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="22px">Our programme offers a unique and exceptional chance for students to
immerse themselves in the <strong>vibrant and diverse culture of Malaysia</strong> while 
<strong>expanding their knowledge</strong>.</mj-text> 

<mj-text font-size="16px" font-weight="300" color="#134473" font-family="Lato,Verdana,sans-serif" align="left" text-decoration="none;"  line-height="22px">Through a variety of activities such as <strong>cultural workshops</strong>, <strong>history lessons</strong>,
as well as <strong>visits to significant cultural and historical sites</strong>, you can gain a 
<strong>profound understanding and appreciation</strong> of <strong>Malaysian customs</strong>, 
<strong>traditions</strong>, and <strong>way of life</strong>.
</mj-text> 

<mj-spacer height="10px" />
        
        
